text: Prashanth Nair (born May 7, 1993) is an Indian-born American cricketer. He made his List A debut for the United States in the 2017–18 Regional Super50 on February 18, 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:American cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Cricketers from Kerala
